    "The majority of Another perspective about blockchain as part of a sustainable transition in leveraging circular data was presented in [41].",
    "The author states that sustainability should be adopted by all interconnected stakeholders in order to produce fully transparent and sustainable products and services.",
    "Moreover, assurance of common goals and leveraged data is essential and manageable through Blockchain technology.",
